targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  count(id) as "NEW\:"
FROM user
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created_at)
ORDER BY created_at

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  count(id) AS "All Time\:"
FROM user

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  count(id) as "Enabled (All Time)\:"
FROM notification
WHERE
  enabled = 1

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  count(id) as "All\:"
FROM notification

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  COALESCE(COUNT(chat_id), 0) as "New (Enabled)\:"
FROM notification
WHERE
  enabled = 1 AND
  $__timeFilter(created_at)

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  count(id) as "NEW\:"
FROM user
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created_at)
ORDER BY created_at

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  count(id) AS "All\:"
FROM user

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  COALESCE(COUNT(user_id), 0) as "NEW\:"
FROM learn_notification
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(created_at)

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  COALESCE(COUNT(user_id), 0) as "Personal\:"
FROM learn_notification_personal

SELECT
  created_at AS "time",
  COALESCE(COUNT(user_id), 0) as "All\:"
FROM learn_notification

SELECT
  deleted_at AS "time",
  COALESCE(COUNT(user_id), 0) as "Not found chat\:"
FROM user_notification
where deleted = 1 and
  $__timeFilter(deleted_at)

SELECT
  deleted_at AS "time",
  COALESCE(COUNT(user_id), 0) as "Not found chat (all)\:"
FROM user_notification
where deleted = 1

SELECT
  version_notification.created_at AS "time",
  version.version as version,
  COALESCE(COUNT(version_notification.chat_id), 0) as users
FROM version_notification
inner join version ON version.id = version_notification.version_id
group by version.version
order by version.version desc

SELECT
  user.updated_at AS "time",
  user.username as UserName,
  user.first_name as FirstName,
  user.last_name as LastName,
  user.id as "user id"
FROM user
WHERE
  is_bot = 0 AND
  $__timeFilter(updated_at)
order by updated_at desc

SELECT 
  count(t.status) as count,
  t.status,
  user.username as UserName,
  user.first_name as FirstName,
  user.last_name as LastName,
  user.id as "user id"
FROM `training` as t join user as user on user.id = t.user_id
where t.status != 'never'
group by t.user_id, status
order by t.status desc, count desc
